File Adoption

Breadcrumb

  1. Home
  2. Administration
  3. Reports
  4. File Adoption

Status message

Configuration saved.
File paths (relative to public://) to ignore when scanning. Separate multiple patterns with commas or new lines.
If checked, orphaned files will be adopted (added to the file management system) during cron runs and when using the Scan Now button.
If checked, and the Media module is installed, adopted files will also be added to the Media library.
Public Directory Contents Preview
  • public:// (e.g., 10089514-21-F - Amendment 1.pdf) (3 orphan files)
  • asset_injector/ (matches pattern asset_injector/*)
  • embed_buttons/ (e.g., embed-view.svg) (matches pattern embed_buttons/*)
  • php/ (matches pattern php/*)
  • private/ (matches pattern private/*)
  • css/* (pattern not found)
  • js/* (pattern not found)
  • webforms/* (pattern not found)
  • config_* (pattern not found)
  • media-icons/* (pattern not found)
  • styles/* (pattern not found)
